gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Cavaliers 119, Raptors 95
gameRecap.excerpt: The Cavaliers win their ninth straight game as they defeat the Raptors, 119-95. Jarrett Allen led the way for the Cavaliers with 18 points and 15 rebounds, while Evan Mobley added 17 points and 11 rebounds in the victory. Scottie Barnes tallied 24 points, 10 rebounds and 10 assists for the Raptors in the losing effort, his third triple-double of the season and fourth of his career. The Cavaliers improve to 35-16 on the season, while the Raptors fall to 19-34.
